{"tid":335221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"財團辦「青年宿舍」　回報料7厘　1600呎22牀分租　毋須領牌","createTime":"2017-07-25T12:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T03:15:14.000Z","uid":112720,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb6a712cd1784f4d0e926d3ff20a04232631b6e","tid":335221,"uid":112720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:00:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170725/s00001/1500919219065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170725%2Fs00001%2F1500919219065&d=ammElTl8ef0XgIZwl6iYv8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e6120a93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170725%2Fs00001%2F1500919219065&h=6a4440c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170725/s00001/1500919219065</a><br />\n<br />\n據該公司提供資料，書匯兩幢大樓樓高5層，其中東安街50號每層分間成6至10個牀位，鄭穎琛說目前已由一間本地大學承租了46個牀位。另登打士街10、12號則設110個牀位，<span style=\"color: red;\">每層設22個牀位（分兩個單位），但每層只有4個淋浴間及4個坐廁（設於公共空間）</span>，房間種類分為單人房、<span style=\"color: red;\">雙人房</span>及「碌架牀」房，租金由3000多元至5000多元（見圖）。<br />\n若以面積最大單人房計，低層月租最貴5000多元，面積約50方呎，折合呎租約100元。公司發言人稱，由於書匯每個單位的牀位不多於11張，故不受《牀位寓所條例》限制（見另稿），不過項目的樓宇結構、消防安全等均符合基本標準。<br />\n<br />\n2"},{"pid":"6ac30a0f3b52776ee438c7dd98749a1a4cf94e07","tid":335221,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:04:14.000Z","msg":"嘩...乞兒竇"},{"pid":"61703b7d7aa17ed7f10b4b0b6ce3caa2e6b813e4","tid":335221,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:04:36.000Z","msg":"連乞兒位都1600"},{"pid":"eb0303c0c712ec8e7c2a05d3b2bd705792043bb3","tid":335221,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連乞兒位都1600</blockquote><br />\n3000"},{"pid":"f19f522b856907c2041a7e8c0724450edf8a315d","tid":335221,"uid":112720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"